        "heading": "Who am I?",
        "paragraphs": [
            "I'm Thiwanka Sandakalum, a passionate Cloud-oriented Software Engineer with expertise in designing and delivering scalable backend systems, distributed microservices, and cloud-native platforms. Based in Colombo, Sri Lanka, I specialize in building secure REST, GraphQL, and gRPC APIs while integrating identity and authentication solutions (Auth0, RBAC/JWT).",
            "My experience spans the full development lifecycle‚Äîfrom architecture and development to deployment, monitoring, and CI/CD automation. I'm particularly skilled in optimizing applications through caching, load balancing, and distributed messaging (Redis, RabbitMQ), ensuring reliability, security, and high performance.",
            "I have a proven track record in e-commerce platforms, back-office systems, and AI-powered solutions, consistently delivering measurable improvements in operational efficiency, system scalability, and user experience. Adept at managing complex projects from conception to production deployment."
        ],
